<center>Figure 6: Agent utility vs attack success rate. (a) Benign utility vs targeted attack success rate. (b) Benign utility vs utility under attack; Points on the Pareto frontier of utility-robustness are in bold. We report \(95\%\) confidence intervals in Table 3. </center>  

<|ref|>image<|/ref|><|det|>[[189, 329, 804, 457]]<|/det|>
